commit.message: Modify changelog and the date of the copyright from the source files. Correction of the man page.

Merge pull request #3 from dmitrysmagin/libmikmod-fix

handler_audio.cc: Don't rely on SDL_mixer using libmikmod
Merge pull request #2 from dmitrysmagin/master-fixes

add .gitignore file
fix #806690 Debian bug: Graphical glitch in boss sprite (thank to Celelibi)

- add .gitignore file
- fix #806690 Debian bug: Graphical glitch in boss sprite (thank to Celelibi)

handler_audio.cc: Don't rely on SDL_mixer using libmikmod

As on different platforms it may use libmodplug.
Instead, use mikmod directly for music and catch output with
Mix_HookMusic().

This is pretty hacky as 'no sound' driver is used with
direct calling to VC_WriteBytes() to fill the buffer.

MikMod_RegisterAllLoaders() fail for some platforms so use
MikMod_RegisterLoader() separately.

Register .xm loader as well as .mod because area1-game2.mod is .xm
in disguise.

configure.ac: Remove checking for malloc

It brings more troubles when cross-compiling and with mingw32.
Anyway, malloc() is not directly used at all.

handler_resources.cc: supervisor_map_editor.cc: Remove WIN32 specific part

_write() falls into eternal loop when compiled with mingw32, but write()
is just fine
configfile.cc: Fix checking USER env var (logic was reversed)

Remove #define SCOREFILE from tecnoballz.h

as it interferes with the same define in handler_resources.cc

configfile.cc: Check if tecnoballz.conf exists and create if it doesn't

This also creates all dirs of the path to tecnoballz.conf
configfile.cc: Fix bug: close file handle after creation.
Adds the missing files.
Fix bug (Debian #776339)  Ball resize not relocated while in corner relaunchers. Thanks to Celelibi for bug reports.

Fix bouncer position restricted in boss levels 
Thanks to Celelibi for the report

Fix bugs (Debian #776342) Buggy Gigablitz jauge.
  Thanks to Celelibi for bug reports 
Fix bugs (Debian #776263) Right click cause game over.
  Thanks to Celelibi for bug reports
add man page
add Debian patchs
prepare 0.93.1 release

add patch from Musuruan 
- make will fail because there is no rule to make supervisor.c
- make install will fail because it cannot find tecnoballz.hi since it's in the parent directory

add README
update AUTHORS
remove tinyxml files (Use tinyxml system library instead)

update man pages
update copyright date
fix bricks collision segfault
fix initialized variables.
fix leak memory
